    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive home a real winner! This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-loved and maintained. It offers a smooth, reliable ride and looks great both inside and out, showing only the minor character you'd expect from a car that's been enjoyed. It's the perfect combination of quality and value for your next adventure!",
